I'll search the repository for authentication-related files using several targeted approaches.

```
shell{"command":"rg -l -t py 'auth|login|password|token|jwt|session|oauth|signin' --ignore-case 2>/dev/null; rg -l --glob '*.ts' --glob '*.js' --glob '*.py' --glob '*.java' --glob '*.go' 'auth|login|password|token|jwt|session|oauth|signin' --ignore-case 2>/dev/null"}
```
```
shell{"command":"rg -l 'middleware|guard|interceptor|authenticate' -g '*.py' -g '*.ts' -g '*.js' -g '*.java' -g '*.go' 2>/dev/null"}
```
```
shell{"command":"find . -maxdepth 4 -type f \\( -name '*auth*' -o -name '*login*' -o -name '*token*' -o -name '*session*' -o -name '*passport*' -o -name '*jwt*' \\) 2>/dev/null | head -30"}
```
